text: Historia Naturalis may refer to: *Natural History (Pliny), a natural history encyclopedia by Pliny the Elder *Historia Naturalis Brasiliae, a book on Brazilian natural history by Willem Piso and Georg Marcgraf published in 1648 *Historia naturalis palmarum, a botanical book by Carl Friedrich Philipp von Martius published between 1823 and 1850
title: Historia Naturalis
